texts.text: *Pant*
>Between the attacks of an endless supply of angelic reinforcements
>and the superhuman Blue Seed's gunfire,
>you've been roughed up pretty bad.

*Sob*
You're at the end of your rope, aren't you.

*Cower*
I-I'm sorry. Please stop this futile resistance...
>You try a surprise attack with your sword, but it's easily parried.
>Breathing heavily, you were able to muster the strength to try again...
P-Please. No more...
>But Blue Seed sends your sword flying with a single blow.
>Faltering, you fall to one knee.
>You're exhausted and unarmed. There's no way for you to fight back anymore...
Poor [sys user_name]...
I think I'll send you off with this gun. It's the least I can do.
To kill you with the gun made by the people you betrayed...
...Ahaha. Ahahahaha. Ahahahahahahahahah!
Say... Goodbyeeeeeeeee!
*Moan*
Yes, this way... Good girl.
*Moan*
>In a trance, Pixie's fingers touch the focal point
>of the electric cage surrounding Jabo.
Yaaaa!
A-AAAARGH!
>...Everything happened in an instant.
>The electric field disappeared as soon as Pixie touched it,
>and before Blue Seed can pull the trigger,
>Jabo closes the distance in a split second and pierces his abdomen with one hand.
U-Ugh...
>Retracting his hand from Blue Seed,
>Jabo grabs him by the neck and raises him up with one hand.
Aaaaagh!
You'll never be the Savior.
You're just the angels' puppet.

*Groan*
Angels...
P-Please help me...
We thought you could be God's weapon, but this is as far as you can go.
...Huh?
We only helped you because we wanted to test you.
Not only did you fail to triumph over adversity, you are begging us for help...
You are not worthy to be a weapon of God, so we do not need to keep you.
Come my brethren, let us return to heaven.
>The angels cease their attack,
>and rise up towards the light parting the clouds.
This can't be! They're abandoning me?!
I'M the hero! Me!

*Pant*
I... I'm...
You're just another human that got played by demons.
A foolish pawn made to think he's the hero.
*Sob*
Hehe... Hahaha...
You're one to talk...
You're just manipulating [sys user_name] as well, right...?
We're doing the same thing to you demons too...

But I have just cause...
Miss Ryuzouji is waiting for me...
>After a series of blood curdling noises,
>Blue Seed falls silent, his sentence unfinished.
>All that was left of him was a gruesome corpse with a severed head.
...Me manipulating [sys user_name]? What a nasty thing to say.
That ticked me off so much that I accidentally popped his head right off.
Our relationship is much deeper than that.
Don't you think so too, [sys user_name]?
>You look into Jabo's emerald colored eyes.
>You have no idea what the man before you is thinking.
...There's something on your mind.
You can say it out loud. We're besties after all.
What are you hiding from me?
Time to come clean. About everything.
Me? Hide something from you?
Never.
Everything? But I already told you all I know.
Everything I can to tell you, and everything you need to know.
>You continue to press him by saying
>"Then what is this Aion that Blue Seed was trying to reach?"
...I was going to tell you, but I just thought that
you should travel this world and see it with your own eyes first.
That's all.
I know, you think I'm just trying to weasel my way out of answering your question right?
But believe me, it's not to hide things from you.
I'm just waiting for the right time.
I promise I'll tell you when the time comes, okay?
Besides, you'll find out soon enough.
Well, it looks like my friend is no longer in danger, so I should go.
Bye, [sys user_name].
You too, little fairy. See you around.
>At Jabo's words, you are reminded of Pixie.
[sys user_name]...
Are you hurt?
You're okay right?
Hurt...? No, but...
Yeah. I'm okay... I think. But...

......
It's nothing...

No, that's not right...
I don't know how to say this, but...
That guy scares me...
He's always smiling, and he's real gentle. But...
>Her head bowed, Pixie clasps her hands together tight to stop them from trembling.
>You turn around to find Jabo already gone.
>The only things in sight are the endless wasteland and the cloudy sky.
